ga - Git Archive

USAGE:
    ga <source-reference> <reference>

DESCRIPTION:
    Create a git archive or delete a reference.

ARGUMENTS:
    source-reference
        Source branch, tag, or git hash

    reference
        Branch, tag, or git hash to archive/delete

EXAMPLES:
    ga main backup
    ga v1.0.0 release
    ga abc123 feature-branch
